import React from 'react'
import { Typography, List, ListItem, IconButton, Grid } from '@mui/material'

//import { styled } from '@mui/material/styles'
import {
  SearchOutlined, LocationOnOutlined, LocalPostOfficeOutlined, ShoppingBagOutlined,
  PersonOutlineOutlined, FavoriteBorderOutlined
} from '@mui/icons-material'



const MediumHeader = ({ title }) => {

  // const MyStyledButton = styled(Button)(({ theme }) => ({
  //   fontFamily: 'Arial',
  //   textTransform: 'lowercase',
  //   padding: theme.spacing(2)
  // }));

  return (

    <Grid container spacing={2} 
    sx={{alignItems:'center',
         padding:'16px',
         margin:'0',
         '&>.MuiGrid-item':{
          padding:0         
          }}}>
      <Grid item xs={2}>
        <List sx={{ display: "flex", flexDirection: "row", alignContent: "center", width:'50%'}}>
          <ListItem>
            <IconButton>
              <SearchOutlined />
            </IconButton>
          </ListItem>
          <ListItem>
            <IconButton>
              <LocationOnOutlined />
            </IconButton>
          </ListItem>
        </List>
      </Grid>

      <Grid item xs={8}>
        <Typography component="h1" sx={{textAlign:'center', textTransform:'uppercase',
         fontFamily:'Aldrich', letterSpacing:'6px', fontSize:'3.2vw'}}>{title}</Typography>
      </Grid>

      <Grid item xs={2}>
          <List sx={{ display: "flex", flexDirection: "row" }}>
            <ListItem>
              <IconButton>
                <LocalPostOfficeOutlined />
              </IconButton>
            </ListItem>
            <ListItem>
              <IconButton>
                <FavoriteBorderOutlined />
              </IconButton>
            </ListItem>
            <ListItem>
              <IconButton>
                <PersonOutlineOutlined />
              </IconButton>
            </ListItem>
            <ListItem>
              <IconButton>
                <ShoppingBagOutlined />
              </IconButton>
            </ListItem>
          </List>
      </Grid>

    </Grid>
      )
}
 
      export default MediumHeader
